               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18381126-name-944" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-944" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-944" type="surname" value="BIRD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-944" type="given" value="WILLIAM JOHN"></interp>WILLIAM JOHN BIRD</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Exmouth-street, Spitalfields, and keep a general sale shop. I employed the prisoner to repair some cabinet work on the 24th of November—I saw him going away at a time he ought not with something under his apron—I followed him to Baker's-row—it proved to be a cruet-stand—this is it—it has been broken up—it cost me from 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. to 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a few days before—the boots I lost, but cannot trace them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
