                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-945" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY BROWN</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a marine-store shop—I bought this article of the prisoner about four o'clock, on the 24th of November—it was bent up double—he said it was a piece of stuff he found among some rubbish—I gave 3 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for it—it was so tarnished that I took a file to file it before I bought it—I thought it was only pewter, but it has been plated.</p>
